            <h2>Privacy Compliance Certification</h2>
        </p>
        <p>
            Appy Health Inc. has HIPAA certification.
        </p>
        <p>
            <h2>Collection of your Personal Information</h2>
        </p>
        <p>
            In order to better provide you with products and services offered on our
            Site, Appy Health Inc. may collect personally identifiable information,
            such as your:
        </p>
        <p>
            - First and Last Name
        </p>
        <p>
            - E-mail Address
        </p>
        <p>
            - Phone Number
        </p>
        <p>
            - Age
        </p>
        <p>
            - Gender
        </p>
        <p>
