        </p>
        <p>
            If you would like to stop receiving marketing or promotional communications
            via email from Appy Health Inc., you may opt out of such communications by
            Uncheck the "I am interested in receiving promotions" checkbox.
        </p>
        <p>
            <h2>External Data Storage Sites</h2>
        </p>
        <p>
            We may store your data on servers provided by third party hosting vendors
